            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mildly elevated HbA1c, indicating impaired glucose regulation or possible prediabetes, despite a low fasting glucose. There is also mild hyperchloremia and low total CO₂, which may suggest a mild metabolic acidosis. Renal function and electrolytes are otherwise within normal limits. Clinical correlation and further evaluation of glycemic control and acid-base status are recommended.</td></tr></table></div>"
